reviewText: I mostly grabbed this as it featured the late Bruno Lawrence, but the quality of this DVD is clearly a VHS to DVD transfer. For the price of this DVD, you would be better served buying a VHS copy and conducting your own VHS to DVD transfer.

This was a movie that was rather difficult to watch due to its subject matter. (incest) However, it was expertly handled, as a ranch hand newly hired to a place discovers the secret between his new boss and the boss's daughter. If you can make it through the first part of the movie, you might be able to make it through the entire thing. I liked it.
